@startuml
title Sueca - Fluxo Futuro (GraphQL + WebSocket realtime sem polling)

actor "Host (Flutter UI)" as Host
actor "Convidado (Flutter UI)" as Guest
participant "GraphQL API (/graphql)" as GQL
control "LobbyService" as Lobby
control "GameService / GameFactory" as GameSvc
control "EventBus" as Bus
control "WebSocketObserver" as Obs
boundary "WebSocket Handler (/ws)" as WSH
control "Hub" as Hub
control "RoomHub(lobby)" as LobbyRH
control "RoomHub(roomId)" as RoomRH
participant "Host WS Client" as HostWS
participant "Guest WS Client" as GuestWS

== 1) Entrada de utilizadores ==
Host -> GQL : mutation createPlayer(nickname)
GQL -> Lobby : CreatePlayer(nickname)
Lobby --> GQL : player (idempotente por nickname)
GQL --> Host : playerId

Guest -> GQL : mutation createPlayer(nickname)
GQL -> Lobby : CreatePlayer(nickname)
Lobby --> GQL : player (idempotente por nickname)
GQL --> Guest : playerId

== 2) Ligacao ao lobby WS ==
Host -> WSH : GET /ws?roomId=lobby&playerId=hostId
WSH -> Hub : AddClient("lobby", hostClient)
Hub -> Hub : GetOrCreateRoom("lobby")
Hub -> LobbyRH : AddClient(hostClient)
WSH --> HostWS : socket ativo

Guest -> WSH : GET /ws?roomId=lobby&playerId=guestId
WSH -> Hub : AddClient("lobby", guestClient)
Hub -> Hub : GetOrCreateRoom("lobby")
Hub -> LobbyRH : AddClient(guestClient)
WSH --> GuestWS : socket ativo

== 3) Criar sala e atualizar lobby realtime ==
Host -> GQL : mutation createRoom(input)
GQL -> Lobby : CreateRoom(...)
alt input invalido
  Lobby --> GQL : erro
  GQL --> Host : erro
else ok
  Lobby -> Bus : Publish(RoomCreated)
  Bus -> Obs : Update(RoomCreated)
  Obs -> Hub : BroadcastToRoom("lobby", RoomCreated)
  Hub -> LobbyRH : Broadcast(payload)
  LobbyRH --> HostWS : event RoomCreated
  LobbyRH --> GuestWS : event RoomCreated
  GQL --> Host : room
end

== 4) Entrar numa sala privada ==
Guest -> GQL : mutation joinRoom(roomId, guestId, password)
GQL -> Lobby : JoinRoom(roomId, guestId, password)
alt password invalida/ausente
  Lobby --> GQL : erro de password
  GQL --> Guest : erro
else ok
  Lobby -> Bus : Publish(PlayerJoinedRoom)
  Bus -> Obs : Update(PlayerJoinedRoom)
  Obs -> Hub : BroadcastToRoom(roomId, PlayerJoinedRoom)
  Obs -> Hub : BroadcastToRoom("lobby", RoomUpdated)
  GQL --> Guest : room
end

== 5) Sala de espera sem polling ==
Host -> WSH : GET /ws?roomId=<roomId>&playerId=hostId
Guest -> WSH : GET /ws?roomId=<roomId>&playerId=guestId
WSH -> Hub : AddClient(roomId, hostClient/guestClient)
Hub -> Hub : GetOrCreateRoom(roomId)
Hub -> RoomRH : AddClient(...)
WSH --> HostWS : socket da sala ativo
WSH --> GuestWS : socket da sala ativo

note over Host,Guest
No fluxo futuro, o frontend deixa de fazer polling GraphQL na sala de espera.
O estado da sala e atualizado por eventos WS (join/leave/delete/start).
end note

== 6) Host inicia jogo ==
Host -> GQL : mutation startGame(roomId, hostId)
GQL -> Lobby : ValidateCanStart(roomId, hostId)
GQL -> GameSvc : StartGameFromRoom(roomId)
GameSvc -> GameSvc : shuffle + deal + define trump + turn order
GameSvc -> Bus : Publish(GameStarted)
GameSvc -> Bus : Publish(InitialTableState)
Bus -> Obs : Update(GameStarted / InitialTableState)
Obs -> Hub : BroadcastToRoom(roomId, events...)
Hub -> RoomRH : Broadcast(payloads)
RoomRH --> HostWS : events de inicio
RoomRH --> GuestWS : events de inicio
GQL --> Host : ok

== 7) Jogada de carta ==
Guest -> GQL : mutation playCard(gameId, playerId, card)
GQL -> GameSvc : PlayCard(...)
alt jogada invalida
  GameSvc --> GQL : erro (fora de turno/regra)
  GQL --> Guest : erro
else jogada valida
  GameSvc -> Bus : Publish(CardPlayed)
  Bus -> Obs : Update(CardPlayed)
  Obs -> Hub : BroadcastToRoom(roomId, CardPlayed)
  Hub -> RoomRH : Broadcast(payload)
  RoomRH --> HostWS : CardPlayed
  RoomRH --> GuestWS : CardPlayed

  opt fim da vaza
    GameSvc -> Bus : Publish(TrickEnded)
    GameSvc -> Bus : Publish(ScoreUpdated)
    GameSvc -> Bus : Publish(TurnChanged)
    Bus -> Obs : Update(...)
    Obs -> Hub : BroadcastToRoom(roomId, ...)
  end

  opt fim do jogo
    GameSvc -> Bus : Publish(GameEnded)
    Bus -> Obs : Update(GameEnded)
    Obs -> Hub : BroadcastToRoom(roomId, GameEnded)
  end

  GQL --> Guest : ok
end

== 8) Cleanup ==
HostWS -> WSH : close
GuestWS -> WSH : close
WSH -> Hub : RemoveClient(roomId, client)
Hub -> RoomRH : RemoveClient(client)
alt room hub vazio
  Hub -> Hub : remove roomId
end

note over GQL,Hub
Padrao alvo:
- GraphQL: comandos e queries de snapshot inicial
- WebSocket: stream de eventos para sincronizacao realtime do estado
end note

@enduml
